Tue Jun  5 12:33:05 CEST 2007 <economop@cwi.nl>
 * src/goto.c: fixed bug #752. We were adding reductions after each follow
   restriction was processed instead of only after all restrictions were
   processed. This led to some reductions being added for lookahead symbols
   that later became invalid. I also optimised the iteration over the lookahead 
   list.
 * test/tables/Follower.tbl: regenerated as the parse table changed.

Mon Jun  4 10:43:30 CEST 2007 <economop@cwi.nl>
